CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

July 10, 2014

[Cite as 0711012014 Case Announcements #2, 2014-Ohio-3054.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-0999. Disciplinary Counsel v. Deters.

This cause came on for further consideration upon respondent’s filing of a motion to supplement the record and a notice to withdraw motion to supplement the record.

Upon consideration thereof, this court orders that the motion to supplement the record is granted. Respondent’s notice to withdraw motion to supplement the record is denied as moot.
